385
00:23:19,931 --> 00:23:21,411
You just need more practice.

386
00:23:23,371 --> 00:23:25,491
Can you use this to draw?

387
00:23:25,811 --> 00:23:28,251
I'll copy your design drafts onto it,

388
00:23:28,251 --> 00:23:29,371
