maybe we could compile it

396
00:23:47,411 --> 00:23:48,771
into a beginner's nursing manual.

397
00:23:49,531 --> 00:23:50,211
Sure.

398
00:23:50,811 --> 00:23:52,251
I can do these things now.

399
00:23:52,811 --> 00:23:53,491
Good.

