00:31:54,891 --> 00:31:56,211
I just misspoke.

546
00:31:56,211 --> 00:31:57,251
I'm really sorry.

547
00:31:57,571 --> 00:31:59,011
Sorry, everyone.

548
00:32:07,851 --> 00:32:09,851
Chen Guangpu, what are you doing?
